Me: &quot;It&#x27;s new with iOS 9. It&#x27;s a little news reader. You tell it what you&#x27;re interested in, and it&#x27;ll show you articles.&quot;
Dad: &quot;Cool&quot; <proceeds to spend an hour with it><p>You may be surprised.
